'''Irving Gordon''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Senior Pairs Championship]] (1) 1998

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (2) 1975, 1998 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (2)
** 0 (2) 1975, 1998 

